  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">AmarMP.com: The gateway to the MP in Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">As we know that Members of Parliament (MP) in Bangladesh have been slow to embrace the benefits of using social media to communicate with their constituents; the project called AmarMP.com is bridging the gap between parliamentary representatives and the citizens of Bangladesh by creating a platform for them to connect. The project will set up a clear and easy to follow mechanism for citizens to actively engage in the democratic processes and hold parliamentary representatives accountable.</narrative>
  </description>
